#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga"
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Dutiyadhāraṇasutta"
msgstr "16. Remembering (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.16:1.1"
msgid "“Dhāretha no tumhe, bhikkhave, mayā cattāri ariyasaccāni desitānī”ti?"
msgstr "“Mendicants, do you remember the four noble truths that I taught?”"

msgctxt "sn56.16:1.2"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, aññataro bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, one of the mendicants said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn56.16:1.3"
msgid "“ahaṃ kho, bhante, dhāremi bhagavatā cattāri ariyasaccāni desitānī”ti."
msgstr "“I do, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.428"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.16:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, bhikkhu, dhāresi mayā cattāri ariyasaccāni "
"desitānī”ti?"
msgstr "“How so, mendicant?”"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Dukkhaṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ desitaṃ dhāremi."
msgstr "“Sir, I remember that suffering is the first noble truth you’ve taught."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.3"
msgid "Yo hi koci, bhante, samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "For if any ascetic or brahmin should say this:"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.4"
msgid "‘netaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yaṃ samaṇena gotamena desitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘What the ascetic Gotama teaches is not the first noble truth of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.5"
msgid ""
"Ahametaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paccakkhāya aññaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ paññapessāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"I’ll reject this first noble truth of suffering and describe another first "
"noble truth of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.6"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.7"
msgid "Dukkhasamudayaṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā … pe …"
msgstr "The origin of suffering … The cessation of suffering …"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.8"
msgid ""
"dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā catutthaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ desitaṃ dhāremi."
msgstr ""
"The practice that leads to the cessation of suffering is the fourth noble "
"truth you’ve taught."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.9"
msgid "Yo hi koci, bhante, samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "For if any ascetic or brahmin should say this:"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.10"
msgid ""
"‘netaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yaṃ samaṇena "
"gotamena desitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘What the ascetic Gotama teaches is not the fourth noble truth of the "
"practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.11"
msgid ""
"Ahametaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paccakkhāya "
"aññaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paññapessāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"I’ll reject this fourth noble truth of the practice that leads to the "
"cessation of suffering and describe another fourth noble truth of the "
"practice that leads to the cessation of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.12"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

msgctxt "sn56.16:2.13"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ khvāhaṃ, bhante, dhāremi bhagavatā cattāri ariyasaccāni desitānī”ti."
msgstr "That’s how I remember the four noble truths as you’ve taught them.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.429"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.16:3.1"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhu."
msgstr "“Good, good, mendicant!"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.2"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, dhāresi mayā cattāri ariyasaccāni desitānīti."
msgstr "It’s good that you remember the four noble truths as I’ve taught them."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ kho, bhikkhu, mayā paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ desitaṃ, tathā naṃ dhārehi."
msgstr ""
"Suffering is the first noble truth I’ve taught, and that’s how you should "
"remember it."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.4"
msgid "Yo hi koci, bhikkhu, samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "For if any ascetic or brahmin should say this:"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.5"
msgid "‘netaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yaṃ samaṇena gotamena desitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘What the ascetic Gotama teaches is not the first noble truth of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.6"
msgid ""
"Ahametaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paccakkhāya aññaṃ dukkhaṃ paṭhamaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ paññapessāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"I’ll reject this first noble truth of suffering and describe another first "
"noble truth of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.7"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.8"
msgid "Dukkhasamudayaṃ kho, bhikkhu … pe …"
msgstr "The origin of suffering …"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.9"
msgid "dukkhanirodhaṃ kho, bhikkhu … pe …"
msgstr "The cessation of suffering …"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.10"
msgid ""
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā kho, bhikkhu, mayā catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ "
"desitaṃ, tathā naṃ dhārehi."
msgstr ""
"The practice that leads to the cessation of suffering is the fourth noble "
"truth I’ve taught, and that’s how you should remember it."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.11"
msgid "Yo hi koci, bhikkhu, samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "For if any ascetic or brahmin should say this:"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.12"
msgid ""
"‘netaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ yaṃ samaṇena "
"gotamena desitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘What the ascetic Gotama teaches is not the fourth noble truth of the "
"practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.13"
msgid ""
"Ahametaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paccakkhāya "
"aññaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ catutthaṃ ariyasaccaṃ paññapessāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""
"I’ll reject this fourth noble truth of the practice that leads to the "
"cessation of suffering and describe another fourth noble truth of the "
"practice that leads to the cessation of suffering.’"

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.14"
msgid "netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr "That is not possible."

msgctxt "sn56.16:3.15"
msgid "Evaṃ kho tvaṃ, bhikkhu, dhārehi mayā cattāri ariyasaccāni desitānīti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how you should remember the four noble truths as I’ve taught them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.16:4.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.16:4.2"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
